# Java Fundamentals 💻☕️

This repository contains exercises and practical examples that cover the **fundamentals of the Java programming language**. It is aimed at students or people who want to reinforce or learn essential Java concepts from scratch.

---

## 📚 Topics Covered

- Basic Java Syntax
- Data Types and Operators
- Control Structures (`if`, `switch`, `while`, `for`)
- Methods and Parameter Passing
- Classes and Objects
- Encapsulation
- Inheritance and Polymorphism
- Method Overloading and Overriding
- Using `this` and `super`
- Constructors
- Arrays and Arrays
- Enums
- Exception Handling (`try-catch-finally`)
- Abstract Classes and Interfaces
- Packages and Visibility (`private`, `public`, `protected`)
- Introduction to JavaBeans and Serialization

---